# -[𝗧𝟵𝟬𝗠 𝘁𝗮𝗻𝗸 𝗺𝗼𝗱𝗲𝗹 𝗶𝗻 𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗴𝗿𝗲𝘀𝘀.... ]-
## (DRIVE SHAFT/DRIVE GEAR) 

---

###𝐌𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐚𝐥𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐢𝐬 𝐮𝐬𝐞𝐝 𝐜𝐮𝐫𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐥𝐲:
-Bi-axial DC motor
   ~800gf Torque/300rpm(3v) 
-Female-Female wire(connector) 
   ~15cm length
-Chipboard(Base) 
   ~1mm thick
-H bridge Motor driver(controlled by MCU(ESP32)) 
   ~ESP32-WROOM-32D(CP2102) 
   ~3v-9v
-popsicle stick(base reinforce) 
-Headers(connection) 
-BBQ stick(axle and side reinforce) 
-Li-Po + Li-ion Battery (for source) 
    ~3.7v/15000mAh(overall capacity)

